8.11	Long_telegram	X Article	The X Article, formally titled The Sources of Soviet Conduct, was published in Foreign Affairs magazine in July 1947. The article was written by George F. Kennan, the Deputy Chief of Mission of the United States to the USSR, from 1944 to 1946, under ambassador W. Averell Harriman.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/George_F._Kennan_1947.jpg/250px-George_F._Kennan_1947.jpg
